test Var2='Vanilla Swirl'
test,Var2='Vanilla Swirl'


c='Ice Cream is my favorite'+'.'
print(c)

Answer:Ice Cream is my favorite.

You cannot do 
c='Ice Cream is my favorite'+ 2
print(c)

ANSWER: TypeError                                 Traceback (most recent call last)
